
Source File Layouts:
All source files should begin with the following Comment Block.

/*
File: FILENAME
Author: AUTHOR NAME <AUTHOR EMAIL ADDRESS>
Homepage: http://blahzdns.sourceforge.net/
Comments:
	Description of the operation of the module.
	Including any known bugs and planned feature changes.
*/

SQL Query Syntax:

All queries should be completely in caps.
Columns selected must always be specified. (NO SELECT *)
Any Updates/Inserts should use mysql_escape_string to sanitize user input
	before being submitted to the DB.

